telephone threats saying the station would be burned down 
he said radio corporacion went off the air shortly after the 
attack monday night for reasons that i do not know 
mrs chamorro took office amid high hopes she could resolve the 
nations economic crisis and its bitter political divisions 
at least 30000 people died in that conflict 
the government suspended talks with the strikers over the 
weekend saying negotiations must deal only with labor issues not 
political topics 
it declared the strike illegal claiming it was politically 
motivated the declaration allows the government to fire striking 
workers 
