kenya she interviewed 
kenya a oneparty state has long been considered one of 
africas most stable and successful nations since early this year 
however moi has come under increasing pressure to allow a 
multiparty system 
clashes between mobs and security forces were reported tuesday 
in and around the towns of kiambu nyeri and githunguri all north 
of nairobi where riot troops fired on suspected demonstrators 
violence also was reported in kangemi and kawangware lowincome 
neighborhoods on nairobis western edge where security forces beat 
people indiscriminately according to residents 
