gas in a fresh attempt to fight smog in the city with the nations 
dirtiest air 
ups has taken the initiative in converting their fleet to this 
alternative fuel source that has proven to be an effective 
combatant to the pollutants that destroy the quality of our air in 
los angeles mayor tom bradley said in a statement lauding the 
program i congratulate the commitment of this company 
in a pilot program the carrier will operate a fleet of 20 
vehicles on natural gas supplied by the southern california gas co 
