in sofia bulgaria at an outdoor rally for democracy attended by 
an audience estimated at 14 million pop singer art garfunkel also 
sang 
it was the most mindboggling experience ive ever had 
seals said people just went on into the distance ive played 
for 300000 at a festival and you could have lost them in the first 
few rows over there 
there are no words to describe something like that 
