affect the trials of other indicted traders said it doesnt 
mean anything 
but defense lawyers said the partial victory was a serious blow 
to the governments investigation 
moskys lawyer elliott samuels had argued during the trial 
that the prosecution represented an overzealous and 
outrageous government attempt to enforce vague trading 
regulations arbitrarily 
id like to think the jury was disturbed about the 
